{
  "title": "Amazon Has A Private Food Brand That Just Launched 100 New Products For Fall",
  "content": "<div><section class=\"PostMainArticle__ScContentSection-sc-27z716-3 dPsALc\">\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ContentMarkdown__ScHTMLContent-sc-1qkx5c8-0 kKjmqj\">\n                    <p>One of the best things about fall is all the food offerings. What's not to love when there's <a href=\"https://littlethings.com/lifestyle/pumpkin-spice-craziness\">pumpkin spice everything</a>,\n                      delicious turkey, and apples galore?</p>\n                  </div>\n                  \n                  <div class=\"ContentMarkdown__ScHTMLContent-sc-1qkx5c8-0 kKjmqj\">\n                    <p>Fall is truly a season of food, and that's why we were so excited to discover Amazon's very own\n                      private food brand <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3ThEExB\">Aplenty</a>,\n                      which just dropped over 100 new products perfect for your autumn festivities. </p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"AdProviderWrapper__ScAdSlot-puahik-0 AdProviderWrapper__ScAdSlotInContent-puahik-2 icnfHh\">\n                    \n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"ContentMarkdown__ScHTMLContent-sc-1qkx5c8-0 kKjmqj\">\n                    <p><a href=\"https://amzn.to/3ThEExB\">Amazon launched Aplenty</a> last\n                      year, but it's currently making headlines for all the new items. We're talking Apple Pie Granola\n                      Clusters, Caramel Pumpkin Spice Popcorn, Pumpkin Spice Granola, Honey Crisp Apple Cider, Truffle\n                      Cheese Crisps, and more. Do we have your attention yet?</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"PostDisclaimer__ScWrapper-jh2k1i-4 dWdCNY\">\n                    <div class=\"PostDisclaimer__ContentText-jh2k1i-0 ebFGMD\">\n                      <div>*Psst: if you choose to purchase an item from this post, <a href=\"https://littlethings.com/\" class=\"Link__DefaultStyledExternalLink-sc-1c4upbo-2 cfLxdh\">LittleThings.com</a> may receive a small cut. Each item and price is up to date\n                        at the time of publication; however, an item may be sold out or the price may be different at a\n                        later date.</div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    \n                    <section>\n                      \n                      <div class=\"ContentMarkdown__ScHTMLContent-sc-1qkx5c8-0 kKjmqj\">\n                        <p>Of course, it's never too late to stock up on things via Amazon, thanks to its fast shipping\n                          and extensive stock, but we would be remiss if we didn't tell you to hurry up and start adding\n                          these items to your cart (the Caramel Pumpkin Spice Popcorn is currently out of stock!).</p>\n                        <p>We will be stocking up on the Chocolate Smores Bites, <a href=\"https://amzn.to/3gn3RIi\">Truffle Oil &amp; Mushrooms Thin and Crispy Pizza</a>, and\n                          the 5-Cheese Mac &amp; Cheese Bites to keep us cozy for fall.</p>\n                        <p>If you're more into the holiday treat vibe, Aplenty will be releasing Sparkling Citrus Punch,\n                          Chocolate Peppermint Granola, Double Chocolate Truffle Hot Chocolate, White Chocolate\n                          Peppermint Popcorn, and more in the coming weeks.</p>\n                        <p>Keep scrolling to check out some of our <a href=\"https://littlethings.com/home/must-have-tablescape-elements-for-fall\">fall\n                            favorites</a> from Amazon's Aplenty brand. </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </section>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    \n                    \n                    <section>\n                      <div class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageWrapper-pfsmq8-2 cDzPUa\">\n                        \n                        <figure class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageBox-pfsmq8-1 iiSspo\"><img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120\" srcset=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=15 150w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=30 300w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=60 600w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=90 900w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120 1200w\" alt=\"71attMcKIYS. SL1500\" sizes=\"1088px\" class=\"ImageLoader__ScImage-ib3a51-0 iqaXeM\">\n                          <img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120\" srcset=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=15 150w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=30 300w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=60 600w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=90 900w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/fJS7FFzatkUXi2Xq7SPdP/144b47c8da33350228174610e78229a8/71attMcKIYS._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120 1200w\" alt=\"71attMcKIYS. SL1500\" sizes=\"1088px\" class=\"ImageLoader__ScImage-ib3a51-0 ZWcqD\">\n                        </figure>\n                        <figcaption class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageCaption-pfsmq8-3 QQtWO font-description\">Amazon\n                        </figcaption>\n                      </div>\n                      \n                      <div class=\"ContentMarkdown__ScHTMLContent-sc-1qkx5c8-0 kKjmqj\">\n                        <p>Review: \"I was surprised at how good these were! They hold up in dips, and are not too\n                          crackely. I found myself eating way past the recommended amount! (LOL).\"</p>\n                      </div>\n                    </section>\n                    \n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    \n                    \n                    <section>\n                      <div class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageWrapper-pfsmq8-2 cDzPUa\">\n                        \n                        <figure class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageBox-pfsmq8-1 iiSspo\"><img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120\" srcset=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=15 150w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=30 300w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=60 600w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=90 900w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120 1200w\" alt=\"81NBWP5GJ7L. SL1500\" sizes=\"1088px\" class=\"ImageLoader__ScImage-ib3a51-0 iqaXeM\">\n                          <img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120\" srcset=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=15 150w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=30 300w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=60 600w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=90 900w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/5unXl22tLPbozP2TKCof1a/0a32e8bedd03d39d1ebb8de450d27920/81NBWP5GJ7L._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120 1200w\" alt=\"81NBWP5GJ7L. SL1500\" sizes=\"1088px\" class=\"ImageLoader__ScImage-ib3a51-0 ZWcqD\">\n                        </figure>\n                        <figcaption class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageCaption-pfsmq8-3 QQtWO font-description\">Amazon\n                        </figcaption>\n                      </div>\n                      \n                      <div class=\"ContentMarkdown__ScHTMLContent-sc-1qkx5c8-0 kKjmqj\">\n                        <p>Review: \"This is my favorite frozen pizza--of ANY brand, and it is absolutely DELICIOUS!!! I\n                          keep one or two in the freezer at all times. I highly recommend it to anyone who hasn't tried\n                          it.\"</p>\n                      </div>\n                    </section>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    \n                    \n                    <section>\n                      <div class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageWrapper-pfsmq8-2 cDzPUa\">\n                        \n                        <figure class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageBox-pfsmq8-1 iiSspo\"><img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120\" srcset=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=15 150w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=30 300w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=60 600w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=90 900w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120 1200w\" alt=\"815G1cl45rL. SL1500\" sizes=\"1088px\" class=\"ImageLoader__ScImage-ib3a51-0 iqaXeM\">\n                          <img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120\" srcset=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=15 150w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=30 300w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=60 600w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=90 900w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/4SlwVfDLFKeXIJPpe5AJWg/06352598729ef6e5da48d850c31f9926/815G1cl45rL._SL1500_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120 1200w\" alt=\"815G1cl45rL. SL1500\" sizes=\"1088px\" class=\"ImageLoader__ScImage-ib3a51-0 ZWcqD\">\n                        </figure>\n                        <figcaption class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageCaption-pfsmq8-3 QQtWO font-description\">Amazon\n                        </figcaption>\n                      </div>\n                      \n                      <div class=\"ContentMarkdown__ScHTMLContent-sc-1qkx5c8-0 kKjmqj\">\n                        <p>Review: \"I’m kind of obsessed with all things feta cheese, so I knew I’d love these and they\n                          didn’t disappoint. They’re good in a pinch when having company, especially with vegetarian\n                          friends… although I tend to make them when I need an indulgent snack. Guilty! 😉.\"</p>\n                      </div>\n                    </section>\n                    \n                  </div>\n                  \n                  <div>\n                    \n                    \n                    <section>\n                      <div class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageWrapper-pfsmq8-2 cDzPUa\">\n                        \n                        <figure class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageBox-pfsmq8-1 iiSspo\"><img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120\" srcset=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=15 150w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=30 300w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=60 600w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=90 900w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120 1200w\" alt=\"81ajCDAbs-L. SL1500\" sizes=\"1088px\" class=\"ImageLoader__ScImage-ib3a51-0 iqaXeM\">\n                          <img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120\" srcset=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=15 150w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=30 300w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=60 600w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=90 900w, https://images.ctfassets.net/f60q1anpxzid/3aWr2WRPNWbsSwBPfe5lwA/ba4545a64e450eb04363992cbabd885b/81ajCDAbs-L._SL1500___1_.jpg?fm=jpg&amp;fl=progressive&amp;q=50&amp;w=120 1200w\" alt=\"81ajCDAbs-L. SL1500\" sizes=\"1088px\" class=\"ImageLoader__ScImage-ib3a51-0 ZWcqD\">\n                        </figure>\n                        <figcaption class=\"PostGalleryItem__ScImageCaption-pfsmq8-3 QQtWO font-description\">Amazon\n                        </figcaption>\n                      </div>\n                      \n                      <div class=\"ContentMarkdown__ScHTMLContent-sc-1qkx5c8-0 kKjmqj\">\n                        <p>Review: \"I used this to make some fall trail mix. Added walnuts, candied pecans, white\n                          chocolate chips, and more pumpkin seeds. It was absolutely amazing - the granola was the\n                          star!\"</p>\n                      </div>\n                    </section>\n                    \n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <div>\n                      <div id=\"rc_cont_217692\" class=\"sc-jrsJWt bHAMtT rc-wc rc-uid-217692 rc-g-dl layout_1\">\n                        \n                        \n                        <div class=\"sc-khIgEk djgmnw\">\n                          <div class=\"sc-hTRkXV enlJuL\">\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                          </div>\n                        </div><img src=\"https://b1sync.zemanta.com/usersync/revcontent/?puid=ZmIwNzgyMWE5MDA3NTM1ZTI3MGIyZDhjY2ZkYzkyYTc%3D&amp;cb=https%3A%2F%2Ftrends.revcontent.com%2Fcm%2Fpixel_sync%3Fexchange_uid%3DZmIwNzgyMWE5MDA3NTM1ZTI3MGIyZDhjY2ZkYzkyYTc%253D%26bidder%3D3%26bidder_uid%3D__ZUID__&amp;rev_dt=166671274